  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要梳理一下零售系统的优惠券发放流程。首先，整个流程应该从Retail_CouponSystem开始，它是触发整个业务的核心节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_CouponSystem"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，Retail_CouponSystem作为起点。那它首先会连接到哪里？是直接处理优惠券，还是需要先检查库存？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_CouponSystem"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "需要先检查Retail_Inventory，确认库存状态。这是一个关键的前置步骤。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_CouponSystem",
        "Retail_Inventory"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把Retail_CouponSystem连接到Retail_Inventory了。接下来从库存检查之后呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_CouponSystem",
        "Retail_Inventory"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "库存检查之后，需要进入一个判断节点，再次回到Retail_CouponSystem进行条件判断——这个判断节点用菱形表示，决定优惠券系统是否可用。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_Inventory",
        "Retail_CouponSystem"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下，这里Retail_CouponSystem既作为起点，又作为判断节点使用，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_CouponSystem"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，判断节点有两个分支：如果优惠券系统不可用（No），流程直接结束，回到Retail_Inventory进行记录；如果可用（Yes），则继续使用Retail_CouponSystem处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_CouponSystem",
        "Retail_Inventory"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加判断节点和两个分支。No分支指向Retail_Inventory，Yes分支继续走Retail_CouponSystem。接下来呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_CouponSystem",
        "Retail_Inventory"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "优惠券系统确认可用后，需要进入Retail_OrderManagement的判断，检查订单管理模块是否正常。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_CouponSystem",
        "Retail_OrderManagement"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Retail_OrderManagement判断节点已添加。它的分支逻辑是什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_OrderManagement"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "如果订单管理不可用（No），流程转到Retail_PointOfSale，直接走收银系统；如果可用（Yes），则需要进一步检查Retail_Inventory的实时库存。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_OrderManagement",
        "Retail_PointOfSale",
        "Retail_Inventory"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，No分支到Retail_PointOfSale，Yes分支到Retail_Inventory判断。这个库存判断是另一个菱形节点吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_PointOfSale",
        "Retail_Inventory"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，Retail_Inventory再次作为判断节点。如果库存不足（No），返回Retail_CouponSystem标记失败；如果库存充足（Yes），进入Retail_OrderManagement正式创建订单。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_Inventory",
